summary: Help I’m v anxious right now and I need something long a chaptered to read, possibly with as little drama as possible. Talking...
question: Help I’m v anxious right now and I need something long a chaptered to read, possibly with as little drama as possible. Talking about phanfic of course
answer:
Hey friend! i’m so sorry you are feeling anxious:( Here’s some happy long fics for you!

Sweet Tooth (E, 21k) by @phantasizeit - I remember this fic being very happy and lovely!

Daniel’s Spaniels (G, 17k) by @northerndownpovr - Almost no drama, just a lot of cute dogs!

Sidetracked (G, 86k) by @phanimist - A bachelorette AU. It has some drama, but very little. Most of all it’s really happy.

No, we’re not calling this fate (M, 24k) by everythingisalot (ao3) - This is a good choice if you want something funny and light. It has a bit of drama, but very very little, mostly it’s just absolutely adorable. 

read between the lines (i will if you will) (M, 72k) by @phanbliss - A 2009 canon fic, which has as much drama as real life had at that moment, but I always feel very happy after reading it!

Hope these help, dear friend! <3

summary: I've been thinking a lot about this today so I wanna share. I think it hasn't really registered yet that the world of Dan and...
body: I’ve been thinking a lot about this today so I wanna share. I think it hasn’t really registered yet that the world of Dan and Phil is gonna change really soon… and not in a bad way. I remember them saying that this tour is most likely the last time they’ll be meeting fans in this kind of setting. They’ll probably stop attending playlist and vidcon too. We always talk about how eventually they’ll get a forever home and a dog and start their family and finally settle down. I think that’s closer than anyone realizes. Once tour is over they are gonna buy a house. They are gonna get a dog. They could actually get married. They might adopt a kid. These ideas we’ve had for so long are going to become reality. And while it might seem crazy to think about it’s actually realistic. Idk I’m just excited for the next chapter.
